# Firebase Hosting public dir — intentionally empty.
# firebase.json rewrites ALL requests ("source": "**") to the Cloud Run
# service `guardian-praeventio` (southamerica-west1). Firebase Hosting acts as
# a pure proxy for the custom domain (app.praeventio.net) + managed SSL; Cloud
# Run serves the SPA + API. No static files are served from here (dotfiles are
# ignored per firebase.json "ignore"). Do not add an index.html here — it would
# shadow the Cloud Run root.
